* Docker for Windows

From https://beta.docker.com/docs/windows/getting-started:
- The current version of Docker for Windows runs on 64bit Windows 10 Pro,
Enterprise and Education (1511 November update, Build 10586 or later).
In the future we will support more versions of Windows 10.

* Gotcha for VirtualBox users on Mac!

- pre-v5 VirtualBox doesn't play well with Docker for Mac (xhyve)
.image images/docker-mac-old-virtualbox.png
- ... so upgrade Virtualbox!
.link https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads

