* Under the covers

- On Mac: xhyve!
- From https://github.com/mist64/xhyve:
```
The xhyve hypervisor is a port of bhyve to OS X.
It is built on top of Hypervisor.framework in OS X 10.10 Yosemite
and higher, runs entirely in userspace, and has no other dependencies.
```
- On Windows: Built on top of Hyper-V

